## Replit

**What is Replit?** 
An online coding platform where you can write, run, and share code without installing anything.

**Why students should use Replit:**
- Works on any device with internet - phone, laptop, iPad
- No setup needed - code runs instantly in browser  
- Easy to share projects with links for group work
- Supports Python, HTML, JavaScript + 50 other languages

**How to get started:**
1. Go to replit.com
2. Create free account with your Gmail
3. Click `Create Repl` → Choose Python → Start coding

**Useful link:** [Replit Documentation](https://docs.replit.com)
